{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"286d5d0b31","title":"“我院党委的党性已失”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d63781f11c","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":17,"articleId":"286d5d0b31"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"249f293b45","name":"北京医学院"},{"id":"8eb85def24","name":"计守勤"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3d080d558e","type":"title","text":"“我院党委的党性已失”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"0e9d49507d","type":"authors","text":"北京医学院计守勤","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"647c6401fe","type":"subtitle","text":"右派分子计守勤仍在顽抗","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"2d11035718","type":"paragraph","text":"〔本报讯〕右派分子计守勤右派立场原封未动，近日来继续顽抗，继续反攻。几日来计守勤贴出了不少东西，现抄录两份如下。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"5a9dc8cdba","type":"subtitle","text":"第一．“我院党委的党性已失”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"c737901331","type":"paragraph","text":"1、违背毛主席的话。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"55d431f68b","type":"paragraph","text":"2、不分敌我。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"342164d72a","type":"paragraph","text":"3、两面手法。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"1ffe920418","type":"paragraph","text":"4、对同志无帮助，只使用。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"666de999eb","type":"paragraph","text":"5、无民主，只集中。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"8e3028d66c","type":"paragraph","text":"6、用歪风来整风。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"9b5ed4def3","type":"paragraph","text":"7、校委会作用不能发挥。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"66c52f0279","type":"paragraph","text":"8、正义未露头，即淹下去了。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"2deacae695","type":"paragraph","text":"9、夸大阶级斗争，助长敌人声势。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"dab409d24b","type":"paragraph","text":"10、高高在上，不能深入下层。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"51a530a7ba","type":"paragraph","text":"11、对事简单粗暴处理。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"041e217ac2","type":"paragraph","text":"12、抹杀人权。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"f32d0621c2","type":"paragraph","text":"无战斗性","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"e11e45f915","type":"paragraph","text":"没打着敌人，伤了自己。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"4fb1ac4638","type":"paragraph","text":"没争取落后，损伤了主动性。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"38d7ab3116","type":"paragraph","text":"整风学习的耽误。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"250e5bc1b6","type":"paragraph","text":"有歪风时躲着，无歪风时放歪风","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"596e564622","type":"paragraph","text":" 红色战士宣","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"0d6808b507","type":"subtitle","text":"第二．“打手”","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"67f6e155ba","type":"paragraph","text":"虽非罪魁，但都是刽子手，一切家破人亡，流离失所，妻离子散的后果，皆是这些人干出来的。这也成了历史的规律了吧！","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"52f8d57a02","type":"paragraph","text":"海螃蟹，很好吃，不去大钳子也可以烹调，但它若惹着了主人，也会先去掉钳子再烹调的，人情都是这样。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"2bbb04125d","type":"paragraph","text":"人有真敢不尊重人情的乱涂原文，甚或揭走式撕毁。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"9a64b9c82a","type":"paragraph","text":"更有的限制人生自由，剥夺发言权，如对院刊不能批评，不得擅离具有私刑性质的会场等言行。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"3158e86511","type":"paragraph","text":"宪法规定了民主权利，言论自由的权利，有人不敢利用，这因有的人对利用者私加打击和抱负。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"45eb2bdee5","type":"paragraph","text":"为着社会主义早日建成，本人敬告今日之打手，别在光天化日之下犯罪了。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"2831c60dff","type":"paragraph","text":" 红色战士宣","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"},{"id":"8c00bb3da8","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：北京医学院出版《北医》，1957年7月17日。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31"}],"page":{"id":"c66b46738a","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"286d5d0b31","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}